The Katsina State Police Command on Tuesday paraded a 17-year-old housewife, Rabi Rabi’u, for stabbing her husband Shamsu Salisu, 25, of Almakiyayi village, Malumfashi Local Government Area of katsina State to death, after an altercation The Katsina state Police Public Relations Officer, Superintendent Gambo Isa, told newsmen at the briefing that the Divisional Police Officer, DPO, for Malumfashi division responded to a distress call based on a report that the victim had an altercation with his wife adding that while he was asleep afterwards, his wife stabbed him with knife in several places in his body including his abdomen which led to his death He said ‘’As a result, he sustained serious injuries. The Police team rushed the victim to Malumfashi General Hospital where he was confirmed dead by the attending physician. ‘’ ‘’ In the course of investigation the police have recovered a sharp knife and a bed sheet all stained with blood. Investigation is ongoing’’. In a related development, the Katsina Police Command has also arrested a 30-year-old man, Samaila Musa of Yan-Nabayye village of Rimi Local Government Area of the state, for constantly chaining and enslaving his two wives; Fatima and Hadiza, before having sexual intercourse with them. According to SP Gambo Isah, the Police Public Relation Officer in the state, while parading Musa alongside other suspected criminals in the commands headquarter, Samaila was arrested based on information gathered by a team of police from Rimi division who uncovered the suspect’s house where he incarcerated his two wives with chains, the Police team also found out that, the suspect was a notorious member of a secret cult group. He said “in the course of investigation, police discovered that the victims have marks and signs of brutalization on their bodies, they defecate on their bodies while in chains, their hairs were cut for ritual purposes and it was also discovered that the suspect also grind pepper and put in their private parts and eyes during their menstrual periods’’. “He usually asked them to clean up used seamen after having intercourse with them, demanded the wives to wash the clothes and drink the water, among other devilish occultist acts being done by the suspect.”